.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, skateboard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Sport      | rugby       | skateboarding |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Transport           | skateboard | train    |
| Music-Genre   | punk           | techno   |

