.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-9::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, frog
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, epic
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Pet   | snake         | frog    |
| Food       | spinach     | cucumber  |
| Hobby      | board-games | chess     |
| Movie-Genre        | epic     | western |

