.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, rock
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, cricket
1. the coach is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b          | rock |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Sport     | cricket            | golf       |

 